<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.6.9">
<l>kīḻmaiyiṉā laṅkōr kīḻmaka ṉiṭṭa muḻaviṉkīḻ</l>
<l>nāḻmaipala colli nīraṇaṅ kāṭum poykāṇkilē</l>
<l>ṉēḻmaippiṟap pukkuñ cēma minnōykku mītēmarun</l>
<l>tūḻmaiyiṟ kaṇṇa pirāṉkaḻal vāḻttumi ṉuṉṉittē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Through baseness, under the drum set up by one low man there,</l>
<l>I can’t see the falsehood of you dancing as demonesses, saying many vain [words].</l>
<l>This [is] the remedy for all this pain [and] protection up to the seventh birth:</l>
<l>according to rule praise, meditating the anklets of lord Kaṇṇaṉ.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
